 floor, the living, dining, and kitchen areas flow seamlessly along the southern axis, framed by expansive glazing that opens to the forest. A newly positioned fireplace anchors the living room, offering panoramic views that extend to Mount Saint Helens on clear days.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563172\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563172\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8-810x1219.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with a leather sling chair and small round table facing large windows overlooking a forest. A wooden ceiling and rug add warmth to the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1219\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8-810x1219.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8-800x1204.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8-768x1156.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8-1021x1536.jpg 1021w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563173\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563173\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-9-810x1287.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with wooden ceiling, skylights, and minimal decor. A gray sofa with a colorful blanket faces two framed artworks on a white wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1287\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-9-810x1287.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Arc