ortland-SHED-Architecture-11-810x1150.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11-800x1136.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11-768x1091.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11-1081x1536.jpg 1081w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563176\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563176\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11m-810x536.jpg\" alt=\"A man, woman, and child sit at a wooden dining table inside a house with large windows showing a forest view.\" width=\"810\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11m-810x536.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11m-800x529.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11m-768x508.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-11m.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563177\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563177\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-12-810x634.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen with wooden cabinetry and ceiling, a central island, and large window overlooking greenery. A wooden dining table with chairs is in the foreground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"634\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-12-810x634.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-12-800x626.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-12-768x601.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe kitchen’s design enhances functionality while celebrating craftsmanship, with custom fir accents and thoughtfully placed windows that connect the space to the landscape. A horizontal window runs along one wall above the cooktop displaying framed views of mature rhododendrons.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563178\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563178\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-13-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen with light wood cabinets, a black countertop, and a large window. A tray with oranges sits on the island.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-13-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-13-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-13-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563179\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563179\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14-810x1114.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with light wood cabinets, black countertop, gas stove, coffee maker, kettle, and decorative items on open shelf. Large window with greenery outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1114\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14-810x1114.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14-800x1101.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14-768x1057.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14-1116x1536.jpg 1116w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563180\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563180\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-15-810x506.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wooden cabinets and a large window showcasing green foliage. Black countertop with a stove, pot, and bowls. Wooden ceiling adds warmth to the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-15-810x506.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-15-800x500.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-15-768x480.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563181\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563181\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a wooden ceiling, large windows overlooking trees, a bed with dark bedding, a leather chair, a nightstand with a plant, and a pair of slippers on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-16-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe primary suite, positioned on the northern side of the house, embodies serene luxury. Featuring a walk-in closet and an elegant bathroom complete with a Japanese soaking tub, it combines comfort with understated elegance. Fir slats above the suite’s entry doors subtly diffuse light, maintaining a connection to the skylight above.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563182\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563182\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17-810x1162.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with wooden accents, large mirror, black countertop, glass shower partition, and black floor tiles.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1162\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17-810x1162.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17-800x1148.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17-768x1102.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17-1071x1536.jpg 1071w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563183\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563183\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18-810x1140.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with wooden cabinets, a black countertop, a large mirror reflecting a wooden ceiling and slats, and a window with a view of green trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1140\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18-810x1140.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18-800x1126.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18-768x1081.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18-1092x1536.jpg 1092w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563184\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563184\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19-810x1282.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden bathtub with a gray towel draped over the edge is positioned by large windows, offering a view of trees. The room has tiled walls and a ceiling light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1282\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19-810x1282.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19-800x1266.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19-768x1216.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19-970x1536.jpg 970w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563185\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563185\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-20-810x548.jpg\" alt=\"A living room with large glass doors overlooking greenery. It has a green couch, a patterned rug, a round ottoman, a wooden rocking toy, and books on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"548\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-20-810x548.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-20-800x541.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-20-768x520.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe renovation also enhances the lower level, turning it into a versatile space for family life. Three flexible rooms – suitable as bedrooms, offices, or fitness areas – accompany a shared bath and a dedicated wine cellar. A cozy lounge, framed by floor-to-ceiling windows, offers a tranquil space for relaxation, reinforcing the home’s strong bond with its natural surroundings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563186\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563186\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-21-810x768.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom interior with a freestanding bathtub, gray tile walls, a towel hanging, and a large window revealing a view of a lush, green forest.\" width=\"810\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-21-810x768.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-21-800x758.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-21-768x728.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=563187\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563187\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-22-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Home gym with a treadmill, stationary bike, and exercise ball is set by large windows displaying a forest view.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-22-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Mori-House-Portland-SHED-Architecture-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more from SHED Architecture \u0026amp; Design, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.shedbuilt.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eshedbuilt.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rafaelsoldiphotography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eRafael Soldi\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n         